<note n="0067002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067002">Kṣaṇika.</note>
<note n="0067003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067003">為＝前【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0067004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067004">自＝目【宋】</note>
<note n="0068001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0068001">便＝隨【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0068002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0068002">上＝下【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0068003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0068003">酢＝醋【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0068004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0068004">現＝見【宮】</note>
